Rock, Paper, Scissors
=====

## Instructions

Your task is to make the classic Rock/Paper/Scissors game against the computer!

Once the functionality is working, apply some styling for that individual touch.

## Pseudo Code

- Create some html for my buttons so that the user can choose what to play
- Going to need a way to get the value of what the user played e.g user played paper...
- Randomise the computer play to give me a value (math.rand?)
- Depending on the two plays, calculate the winner and increment the winners score

you played paper, bot played rock

optional - clear button
